geners@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ellen-degeners@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ellen-degeneres">艾伦·德杰尼勒斯</a>和她的妻子已经搬到英国，很可能“永远”不会回到美国。</p><p>一位与这对夫妇关系密切的匿名消息人士告诉<a href="https://www.thewrap.com/ellen-degeneres-moved-great-britain-left-united-states-donald-trump/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Wrap</em></a> ，德杰尼勒斯和波蒂亚·德罗西已经搬到了英国科茨沃尔德地区，并将他们位于加利福尼亚州蒙特西托的房产挂牌出售。据消息人士透露，这对夫妇永远不会返回美国。 </p><figure id="attachment_3796882" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3796882" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3796882" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Ellen-CREDIT_-Photo-by-ROBYN-BECK_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="艾伦·德杰尼勒斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Ellen-CREDIT_-Photo-by-ROBYN-BECK_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Ellen-CREDIT_-Photo-by-ROBYN-BECK_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Ellen-CREDIT_-Photo-by-ROBYN-BECK_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Ellen-CREDIT_-Photo-by-ROBYN-BECK_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Ellen-CREDIT_-Photo-by-ROBYN-BECK_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Ellen-CREDIT_-Photo-by-ROBYN-BECK_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3796882" class="wp-caption-text">艾伦·德杰尼勒斯（Ellen DeGeneres）——图片来源：ROBYN BECK/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>消息人士称，此举主要是由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>本月早些时候赢得了总统选举。如果属实，这将使德杰尼勒斯成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-trump-on-cusp-of-us-election-victory-entertainment-world-reacts-3809992">继即将上任的总统获胜</a>后第二个逃离该国的知名人士。</p><p>上周，据报道， <em>《绝望主妇》</em>主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/eva-longoria-has-moved-out-of-dystopian-us-following-trumps-election-win-3813056">伊娃·朗格利亚已经搬出美国，在西班牙和墨西哥两地生活</a>。朗格利亚解释了她的举动：“我很荣幸。我要逃离并去某个地方。大多数美国人就没那么幸运了。他们将被困在这个反乌托邦的国家，我的焦虑和悲伤都是为了他们。”她已经有一段时间没有住在洛杉矶了，但她解释说，特朗普的胜利坚定了她减少在这座城市以及整个国家停留时间的愿望。</p><p>至于德杰尼勒斯，在她最后一次单口喜剧巡演结束以及她的 Netflix 喜剧特辑上映后，她就退出了聚光灯， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/ellen-degeneres-new-netflix-special-is-getting-destroyed-by-critics-3796861">该特辑受到了评论家的严厉批评</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3773781" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3773781" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3773781" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ellen-DeGeneres-2024.jpg" alt="艾伦·德杰尼勒斯（Tasos Katopodis/Getty Images for Live Nation 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ellen-DeGeneres-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ellen-DeGeneres-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ellen-DeGeneres-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ellen-DeGeneres-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ellen-DeGeneres-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ellen-DeGeneres-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3773781" class="wp-caption-text">艾伦·德杰尼勒斯（Tasos Katopodis/Getty Images for Live Nation 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>在这部特别节目中，她谈到了<em>Buzzfeed News</em> 2022 报道中针对她的欺凌指控，这<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/ellen-degeneres-is-ending-her-talk-show-next-year-2939364">导致她在播出 19 年后突然结束了脱口秀节目</a>。员工指责高管营造“有毒的工作场所”环境，并指控发生不当性行为、种族主义和欺凌事件。</p><p>指控公开后不久，德杰尼勒斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/ellen-degeneres-apologises-for-toxic-work-environment-as-show-re